{"type":"header","kind":"domain","name":"vsco","mk":2,"perspective":"peer","origin_repo":"lumiere","consumers":["n6-architecture"],"goal":"hexa-vsco surface — physical-limit pro photo editor (verb: EDITS-LIBRARY-DISCOVER, sister to camera APPLIES). Full VSCO feature parity (200+ filter library / HSL / tone curve / recipe / Studio / Discover / Free vs Pro) PLUS 7 alien-grade-10 differentiators: LPIPS ≤ 0.15 / SSIM ≥ 0.95 / PSNR ≥ 35 dB mathematical bounds + 16.67 ms editor latency + 30-min FILTER-ALGEBRA inverse-problem auto-generation + algebra plaintext Recipe + on-device privacy + 7 physics-based tools (Hurter-Driffield 1890 / Wiener 1949 / Cox 1955 / Planck 1900 / cos⁴θ / MacAdam 1942 / CIE 1931) + open marketplace 70% creator royalty. Internal dependency: filter_algebra engine layer (sister .roadmap.filter_algebra cond.2/3). F-VSCO-MVP-1..5 falsifier closure vs iPhone 15 Pro + cloud-sync 99.999% reliability.","required_conditions":[{"id":"vsco.cond.1","desc":"Spec absorbed + 21-section template (own#15 HARD) + own#33 ai-native-verify-pattern Block A-G + 7 differentiators framing","verifier":{"type":"script","path":"docs/vsco/hexa-vsco.md","exit_zero_means_met":true,"status_emit":"§7.1 Block A-G + own#15 21-section + 7 differentiator IPS framing PASS"},"status":"met","evidence":["docs/vsco/hexa-vsco.md (spec absorbed from n6-architecture, alien-grade 10 PHYSICAL-LIMIT)"],"blocker_reason":""},{"id":"vsco.cond.2","desc":"Editor surface — 200+ filter library browser + HSL panel + tone curve + Recipe (algebra plaintext expression like `f = portra ∘ vignette(0.3) ∘ grain(0.2)`) + Studio + Discover tab + Free/Pro tier gate","verifier":"","status":"unmet","evidence":[],"blocker_reason":"mk2 — substantial UI cycle (5 tabs / 200+ filter cells / HSL real-time slider); depends on filter_algebra.cond.2 runtime"},{"id":"vsco.cond.3","desc":"50 inaugural filters auto-generated via FILTER-ALGEBRA inverse problem (30-min batch from N=5 reference image pairs each, vs VSCO 1-2-wee